				<td colspan="2"><span>I agree with everyone here pretty much.  The skills are very important to maintain and you may find yourself getting great items and not have the necessary skill to utilize it without losing a few hundred attack points.
<br />

<br />
My suggestion is get 2 rusties of each kind (1hs, 1hp, 1hb)...go to west Commons, pull the orc centurions and attack with those crap weaps.  Play haste if you have it...lol, I saw my skills rising every 30 seconds and it takes a bit to kill the mob.  They are so low they hardly affect you, so it's a win win situation.  
<br />

<br />
Get temp and max skills in a few hours of standing there swinging away.  You get skills up on each even if it doesn't land, so it's not hard to get each maxed and when you get a great item like you have found 2, they will be useful for you and not making you lose atk.
<br />

<br />
imho, of course,
<br />

